OL,3,CPoll reveals nearly half in Wales
OL,4,Cwould scrap plan supporting refugees
OL,6,FVoters would scrap a scheme aimed at
OL,7,Fsupporting refugees to resettle and
OL,8,Fintegrate into the community, an ITV
OL,9,FCymru Wales poll reveals.
OL,11,FNearly half (49%) of those polled said
OL,12,Fthey'd scrap the Welsh Government's
OL,13,F'Nation of Sanctuary' plan, which
OL,14,Ffocuses on the devolved areas linked
OL,15,Fto supporting those seeking refuge in
OL,16,Fthe country.
