OL,3,CPoll reveals nearly half in Wales
OL,4,Cwould scrap plan supporting refugees
OL,6,FBack in May, Reform UK leader Nigel
OL,7,FFarage told ITV Wales' Sharp End
OL,8,Fprogramme that the Senedd Election in
OL,9,F2026 would be his "priority'. In the
OL,10,Fsame interview, he was asked whether
OL,11,Fhe'd 'keep' or 'scrap' a selection of
OL,12,FWelsh policies. Mr Farage said the
OL,13,FNation of Sanctuary Plan should go "in
OL,14,Fthe bin", dubbing it "absolutely
OL,15,Fbonkers".
OL,17,FIn Tuesday's (September 23) First
OL,18,FMinister's Questions, Welsh
OL,19,FConversatives leader Darren Millar
OL,20,Fcalled for the Nation of Sanctuary
OL,21,Fpolicy to be scrapped.
