OL,6,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan replied:
OL,7,F"This dog-whistle politics of trying
OL,8,Fto compete with Reform is not going to
OL,9,Fget you anywhere, Darren, and you know
OL,10,Fit. You know it. And let me tell you:
OL,11,Fyou were in the front line of people
OL,12,Ftelling us that we had to hold out our
OL,13,Fhand and help the people of Ukraine.
OL,14,FYou were the first person there.
OL,15,FThat's where the nation of sanctuary
OL,16,Fmoney is going. The vast, vast
OL,17,Fmajority of it was spent on supporting
OL,18,Fpeople from Ukraine for years and
OL,19,Fyears."
