OL,6,FAndrea Cleaver, CEO of Welsh Refugee
OL,7,FCouncil, said: "We've seen a handful
OL,8,Fof politicians calling for the Nation
OL,9,Fof Sanctuary to be scrapped, but what
OL,10,Fwe haven't seen is why.
OL,12,FShe added: "When I speak to
OL,13,Fcommunities they say they want to see
OL,14,Fpeople integrate, they want them to
OL,15,Flearn English and Welsh, they say that
OL,16,Fthey want (refugees) to contribute to
OL,17,Fsociety and that they want them to
OL,18,Flive independently.
