OL,6,F"The Nation of Sanctuary plan is
OL,7,Fessentially doing all of that. It's
OL,8,Fproviding access to English language
OL,9,Fclasses and some Welsh classes, it's
OL,10,Fproviding volunteering pathways and
OL,11,Fit's helping for example people who
OL,12,Fmight have qualifications as a doctor
OL,13,For nurse to re-do those qualifications
OL,14,Fso that they can be used in our NHS."
OL,16,FPressure grew over the summer about
OL,17,Fthe crisis facing the UK Government
OL,18,Fover small boats after protests
OL,19,Fcontinued outside asylum hotels,
OL,20,Fincluding in Wales.
