OL,4,Cwould scrap plan supporting refugees
OL,6,FSyrian refugee Noah Bakour, who has
OL,7,Fresettled in Cardiff, says he "doesn't
OL,8,Fblame" people for reacting or
OL,9,Fprotesting.
OL,11,F"They are reflecting what they feel,"
OL,12,Fhe said.
OL,14,F"People aren't doing well due to the
OL,15,Feconomy in the United Kingdom and they
OL,16,Fthink refugees and migrants have taken
OL,17,Fover. Migrants are a blessing for any
OL,18,Fcountry if you have the right
OL,19,Fmanagement for migration and sadly, in
OL,20,Fthe UK, there is no system for
OL,21,Fintegration."
