OL,6,FMr Bakour, was forced to flee his home
OL,7,Fcountry in 2020 due to the civil war.
OL,8,FWhen he arrived in Wales, he couldn't
OL,9,Fspeak English but started volunteering
OL,10,Fin a community garden.
OL,12,FHe said: "I'm grateful for Wales and
OL,13,FCardiff for this sense of welcoming.
OL,15,F"If you asked an asylum seeker if
OL,16,Fyou're happy living in a hotel most
OL,17,Fwould say "of course not". Most people
OL,18,Fwant to integrate, most people want to
OL,19,Flive like a human being.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
