OL,6,F"Most refugees come from places like
OL,7,FSyria or Sudan where there is a
OL,8,Fconflict already - so they may have a
OL,9,Fpassport but they cannot travel to any
OL,10,Fcountry and there is no safe route for
OL,11,Fthem to apply and come to the UK.
OL,13,F"From living here in Wales I've met
OL,14,Fmany refugees who are doctors,
OL,15,Flawyers, engineers - they have very
OL,16,Famazing careers but there is no system
OL,17,Ffor refugees to translate all of this
OL,18,Fdocumentation.
